&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exemplary listening, communication and collaboration skills, with an established ability to work&amp;nbsp;cross-functionally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent problem-solving and decision-making skills, with a focus on customer satisfaction and&amp;nbsp;efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in technical installations, troubleshooting, root-cause identification, corrective and&amp;nbsp;preventive process improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
